<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans I. von Wildenstein zu Wildenfels</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Herausgabe von fünf Ballen Schalaun des Konrad Ostermann, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_136" id="67v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_136_r2l4">Hanſen von VVildenſtein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l5">cʒu wildenfels / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_136_r2l6"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wıldenſtein<ex>er</ex></expan> / Als wir euch vor etvvydick <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> habe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l7"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / die Jr <expan>aufgehalt<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd gen VVildenſtein gefürt habt / Jſt <expan>yecʒu<ex>n</ex>d<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l8">für vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>Oſt<ex>er</ex>man</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / vnd hat vns geſagt / vvie er ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l9">beÿ <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> habe / fünff Schalawn in <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> Plählein <expan>gepunde<ex>n</ex></expan> hab / vnd hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l10">der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vor vns cʒu <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan> behabt / daʒ <expan>dieſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> fünff <expan>Schal<ex>awn</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l11">als die in dem pleͣhlein <expan>v<ex>er</ex>punde<ex>n</ex></expan> ſind / ſein vnd <expan>ander<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> ſein / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l12">Alſo / daʒ kein <expan>auſʒma<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> teil noch gemain daran hab / <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l13"><expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>dieſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſein habe <expan>onhind<ex>er</ex>nuſſe</expan> <expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan> laſʒen wollet / Als etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l14">das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> iiij̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> viti Anno x<hi rend="sup">o</hi> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_136" id="67v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen von Wildenstein czu Wildenfels</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Wildenstein<ex>er,</ex></expan> als wir euch vor etwydick
                                <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> habe
                                <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> die ir
                            <expan>aufgehalt<ex>en</ex></expan> und gen Wildenstein gefürt habt, ist
                                <expan>yeczu<ex>n</ex>d<ex>en</ex></expan> für uns
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Ost<ex>er</ex>man</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger,</ex></expan> und hat uns gesagt, wie er bey
                                <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> habe fünff schalawn in
                                <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> plählein
                            <expan>gepunde<ex>n</ex></expan> hab, und hat der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vor uns czu <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan> behabt, daz
                            <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> fünff
                        <expan>schal<ex>awn</ex></expan>, als die in dem pleͣhlein
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>punde<ex>n</ex></expan> sind, sein und
                                <expan>ander<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> sein, also daz kein
                            <expan>auszma<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> teil noch gemain daran hab.
                                <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> sein habe <expan>on
                            hind<ex>er</ex>nusse</expan>
<expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan> laszen wollet. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        iiii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Viti anno x<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
